Application Metadata Registry

http://microservices.io/patterns/externalized-configuration.html
https://github.com/cer/microservices-examples
http://microservices.io/patterns/service-registry.html
https://github.com/Netflix/eureka/wiki/Eureka-REST-operations

App > Instance > Metadata

Attrs

instanceId
appName
key
value

Endpoints

GET  /apps                                               - get all apps
GET  /apps/appName                                       - get all instances of this app
POST /apps/appName                                       - register a new Application

GET  /apps/appName/instances/instanceId                  - get all metadata for this specific instance ipAddress
POST /apps/appName/instanceId                            - register a new instanceId

GET  /apps/appName/instances/instanceId/metadata/keyName - return the configuration required
PUT  /apps/appName/instances/instanceId/metadata - create or update a metadata entry

Possible metadata

nonSecurePort
securePort
virtualHostname
secureVirtualHostname
hostName
ipAddress
statusPageUrlPath
statusPageUrl
homePageUrl
healthCheckUrl
secureHealthCheckUrl